description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Put your stacking abilities to the test with Pellets QuadraStack.  Stack as many pellets as you can without stacking yourself into a hole.  Then, compare your score to other players.
